    "  distanceMeters        â†’ Optional offset for relative placement. Use with phrases like \"within 500m of\", \"next to\", \"just above\", \"left of\", etc.",
    "  force                 â†’ \"friendly\" | \"enemy\" | \"host-nation\" | \"civilian\"  (default: \"friendly\")",
    "  name                  â†’ Display name, e.g. \"PRC-163 Alpha\", \"Radio 1\"",
