    "  frequencyMHz          â†’ Operating frequency in MHz (REQUIRED â€” no default)",
    "  powerW                â†’ Transmit power in watts (REQUIRED â€” no default)",
    "  antennaHeightM        â†’ Antenna height above ground in meters",
    "  antennaGainDbi        â†’ Antenna gain in dBi",
