    "  Doodle Labs Mesh Rider 915:             frequencyMHz=915, powerW=1, antennaHeightM=1.5, antennaGainDbi=2, receiverSensitivityDbm=-98, systemLossDb=1.5  (MANET, waveform Mesh Rider, ~20 Mbps, up to 10 hops)",
